# TransformResolveSystem

## Purpose
Engine tier of transform resolution. Applies transform change requests to the canonical transform
components, and is the sole adder and writer of PositionComponent, RotationComponent, ScaleComponent,
and LocalBoundsComponent. Reads the single aggregated app request (ResolvedTransformRequestOneFrameComponent,
emitted by the SandboxApp transform resolve tier) and engine-origin requests
(CameraTransformRequestOneFrameComponent, emitted by CameraSystem). For each requested entity it
writes the dirty channels in place when the component already exists, or adds the component
(deferred) on first request. Requests carry absolute values; they do not accumulate.

## Input Components
| Component | Access |
|---|---|
| ResolvedTransformRequestOneFrameComponent | read |
| CameraTransformRequestOneFrameComponent | read |
| PositionComponent | write |
| RotationComponent | write |
| ScaleComponent | write |
| LocalBoundsComponent | write |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| PositionComponent | write / add (deferred) | written in place when present; added deferred on first request |
| RotationComponent | write / add (deferred) | quaternion orientation |
| ScaleComponent | write / add (deferred) | |
| LocalBoundsComponent | write / add (deferred) | local-space AABB min/max |
